&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://software.intel.com/content/www/us/en/develop/articles/intel-sdm.html&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Intel 64 and IA-32 Architectures Software Developer Manuals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

